record.title: GENERAL LEAVE

speaking-unknown-id.title: Mr.
speaking-unknown-id.name: OBERSTAR
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that all Members may have 5 legislative days within which to revise and extend their remarks and include extraneous materials on the conference report on H.R. 1495.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Minnesota?
